<item>
            <title>[LU-9911] lnet_peer_discovery_complete() must use safe list iteration</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9911</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In &lt;tt&gt;lnet_peer_discovery_complete()&lt;/tt&gt; we must use &lt;tt&gt;list_for_each_entry_safe()&lt;/tt&gt; since &lt;tt&gt;lnet_finalize()&lt;/tt&gt; may remove the message from the pending message list. There should also be an assertion at the end of the function that the pending list is empty.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
